al/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身都唔諗住講<br />\n間野尋日仲要搵人打黎兇鳩我 <br />\n沖相沖到好似借大耳窿都第一次見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/115605_5a25b1e0dcc2637490171e66ed894284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F115605_5a25b1e0dcc2637490171e66ed894284.jpg&h=cb06ef14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0532e563f6b752a98d24d712d71ee7db6978fd7","tid":128780,"uid":11841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見for the art fb話比人偷拍所以報左警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪講緊呢單野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都諗緊去唔去備案 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家好驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e529b62b04d93ceaa8460d8cb40bb7060a26e4","tid":128780,"uid":7955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見for the art fb話比人偷拍所以報左警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪講緊呢單野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都諗緊去唔去備案 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家好驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n先去消委會投訴　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff755afc0a9d27a1086152d1599883f0f9e2da1","tid":128780,"uid":20390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T04:29:28.000Z","msg":"間店真係好小家，張相有乜咁大不了，唔講以為係中情局，痴痴地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42cf0f60657bbdb3e4eedc824c20ad6738b80dd","tid":128780,"uid":46035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"推到佢仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ae09a659fefd40