<br />\n所以間野走去報警係極 on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你又咁wor <br />\n我都無留意佢前言不對後語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都無話過佢質素低<br />\n但又此地無銀到要重申佢地高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋我連佢肖像都無影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4078b76472b8a851deb2d6053eb618ab2703cb","tid":128780,"uid":34242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:32:47.000Z","msg":"John講野有時把口好似食左屎咁<br />\n賣點係部scan 無他了"},{"pid":"7b8b6daf35a127283e6e0f9b9cfa35f7eaebac1b","tid":128780,"uid":11638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:34:47.000Z","msg":"點解一件咁簡單既事都可以搞到有花生食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c590916a4195ce62bc1def25387411d3f4b59f","tid":128780,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:46:17.000Z","msg":"已經見到del comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d786c124ecfe87ffd68d9731e81faef93bdf9e59","tid":128780,"uid":11841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>John講野有時把口好似食左屎咁<br />\n賣點係部scan 無他了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晏就去金x scan <br />\n20分鐘搞掂 <br />\n$30<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Nbb8D1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Nbb8D1.jpg&h=404c1d50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"987c7cbd28d81073850bd85d41d0f7173bb8bc18","tid":128780,"uid":11841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:31:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經見到del comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown